						<p>On a slab lying near the ruined Mātangēśvara temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Records the gift of 25 cows to the temple of Mātaṅgēśvara at Śriparvata for burning a perpetual lamp by Bayyapa-Nāyaka, son of Lakshmaṇa-Nāyaka.</p>						

